VOICING PLAN:
- Eb major: I=Eb, ii=Fm, iii=Gm, IV=Ab, V=Bb, vi=Cm.
- Non-diatonic substitutions: "C" major chord → Cm (vi);
  "F" major chord → Fm (ii); "F7" chord → Fm7 (ii7).
- Phrase 1 (mm.1-10): Intro with rests (m.1), then flowing
