  RH dyads, moving with stepwise contrary motion.
- Phrase 2 (mm.11-20): Same material, fuller. LH gains 4th note
  by m.12 (V7 voicing Bb2-F3-Bb3-D4). RH broken arpeggios.
- Phrase 3 (mm.21-29): Bridge section. Gm (iii) chord adds color
